

Use of Final Keyword
a)Final keyword is use to define constant values.
b)it is also use to prevent inheritance
c)to prevent method overriding


Use of finally block

finally
{
}
a)finally block is mostly used after try-catch block 
b)It is bound to execute even if there is an exception or no exception.
c)Even if we are not catching exception properly lets suppose code is throwing ArithmeticException and we are catching 
NullPointer exception then in that case too Finally block will be executed.

Use of finalize method
finalize()
{
}

finalize method will be called to perform some clean up processing






